article_title: Suu Kyi Says She Will Lead Myanmar If Her Party Wins Election

twitter.description: Myanmar opposition leader Aung San Suu Kyi said on Wednesday if her party wins coming elections she will lead the country from behind the scenes, circumventing a clause in the constitution that bars her from the presidency.
twitter.title: Suu Kyi Says She Will Lead Myanmar If Her Party Wins Election
